            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/fecf535e6323269f/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-fecf535e6323269f-f09fcd twpub-fecf535e6323269f-6b4cd0\"><p>For additional contact information:<br>\n\n     Dr. Gregory B. Newby<br>\n\n     Chief Executive and Director<br>\n\n     gbnewby@pglaf.org<br>\n</p></div>"
