            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/fecf535e6323269f/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-fecf535e6323269f-f09fcd twpub-fecf535e6323269f-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
